item.title: Create Dynamic Application Packages with PowerShell
item.description: Dynamic? In what way? When I say the packages are dynamic, I mean that you don’t have to update the application package when a new version is released by the vendor. There are caveats to both methods that we walk through below, there are also other community and paid for tools to do similar things.
